text: Brice Clotaire Oligui Nguema is a Gabonese politician and military officer. He became the Transitional President of Gabon by replacing his cousin, Ali Bongo Ondimba and putting him under house arrest in a 2023 coup. He then won the 2025 presidential election by a wide margin. ==References== Category:1975 births Category:Living people Category:Presidents of Gabon Category:Military people
